race.comment: Open race to close out the card. CLUBHOUSE (3) goes well for hoop Mallyon who has a win and three placings from seven steers and has been thereabouts in recent efforts. Well placed in this assignment and is a must include. FUTURE SOLDIER (1) has been racing well at Toowoomba and winning rider Wilson-Taylor reunites. Top-three aspirations. KRUMAC (13) was a dominant Taroom winner two back before hitting the frame at Warwick last time out. In the mix. QUEST OF QUESTS (2) strips fitter second-up from the break and may earn some minor money as may BEE EXACT (10) who will also be fitter third up and can contest for a place.
